OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy start,
OL,6,Fespecially across Derbyshire hills.
OL,7,FTurning bright, with some sunny spells
OL,8,Flater in the day. Winds easing. Warm
OL,9,For very warm temperatures.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy over Derbyshire hills
OL,12,Fwith mist and light drizzle. Clear
OL,13,Fspells further east allowing some mist
OL,14,Fpatches to form. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,17,Fsome mist and light rain over hills.
OL,18,FTurning brighter through the
OL,19,Fafternoon, especially further east
OL,20,Fwhere it will be very warm. Light
OL,21,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
